list.name: Pump Faults
list.rawQuery:
SELECT
  extract(epoch from time) AS time,
  "pump_fault" as text
FROM
  "SeaFlowInstrumentLog_raw"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) and
  "pump_fault" IS NOT NULL

list.name: Write EVT ON
list.rawQuery:
SELECT
  extract(epoch from time) AS time,
  "write_evt" as text
FROM
  "SeaFlowInstrumentLog_raw"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) and
  "write_evt" = 1

list.name: Write EVT OFF
list.rawQuery:
SELECT
  extract(epoch from time) AS time,
  "write_evt" as text
FROM
  "SeaFlowInstrumentLog_raw"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) and
  "write_evt" = 0

list.name: Flagged during filtering
list.rawQuery:
SELECT
  extract(epoch from time) AS time,
  "file_flag" as text
FROM
  "SeaFlowSFL_raw"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) and
  "file_flag" != 0

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("time",$__interval),
  avg(event_rate) AS "event_rate",
  avg(all_count/180) AS "calculated_event_rate"
FROM "SeaFlowSFL"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time")
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("time",$__interval),
  avg(abundance) AS "beads per µL"
FROM "SeaFlowPopAbundance"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time") AND
  pop = 'beads'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1
